item.title: Prayer bpn10230 in Māori
item.description: *Ka uru ana koe ki roto o te whare kaunihera, whakatātakina tēnei inoi ki te manawa kakapa, te aroha o Te Atua, me te arero harakore i tua atu o te katoa ēngari mō Tōna maumaharatanga, ka tau mārire ai te āwhina a Te Pūkaha-Katoa kia ekea e koe te taumata tonu o te wikitōria. E Te Atua, tōku Atua! Ko mātou he pononga Nāu kua tahuri me te piripono ki Tōu kanohi tapu, kua wetekina mai i te katoa i tua atu i a Koe ki tēnei Rā korōria.
